Projects

This Website

I created this website from scratch in Javascript. I used React, Gulp, Sass, and Bootstrap in the process of creating this website. Additionally, I familiarized myself with Github and Github pages in order to host this page online.

School Assignments

At OSU, I have completed projects in various languages, both alone and as part of a team working within an Agile framework.

Legend of Zelda: C#

As part of a team of 5 students, I helped create a remake of the first dungeon in Legend of Zelda for the NES. We used C# and our work was divided into sprints with the project requirements changing every 3 weeks. As a team, we had to determine our plan of action during our scrums and then complete the necessary work in a maintanable fashion so we could pivot when the next sprint began.
